title: Aulonocara brevirostre
text: Aulonocara brevirostre is a species of <a href="haplochromine">haplochromine</a> <a href="cichlid">cichlid</a> which is <a href="Endemism">endemic</a> to <a href="Lake%20Malawi">Lake Malawi</a>. It is found along the eastern shore of the Lake in Malawi, Mozambique and Tanzania. It is common at depths of , it has been found to feed on small invertebrates. algae and detritus.
